# Team-OS Hub (Local)

This directory is generated by deterministic Team-OS pipelines.

- Root: `{{HUB_ROOT}}`
- Postgres: `{{PG_BIND_IP}}:{{PG_PORT}}`
- Redis (required): `{{REDIS_BIND_IP}}:{{REDIS_PORT}}`

## Commands

```bash
openteam hub init
openteam hub up
openteam hub migrate
openteam hub status
```

Remote exposure is high risk and must be approved:

```bash
openteam hub expose --bind-ip <private-ip> --allow-cidrs "10.0.0.0/24" --open-redis
```
